---
title: Nacho Style Loaded Chorizo Fries and Tomato Salsa with 'Queso' Cheese Sauce and Chipotle Black Beans
description: Load up on flavour with our Nacho Style Chorizo Loaded Fries and Tomato Salsa for a delicious dinner. The main flavour here comes from chipotle, full of rich, smoky and fruity flavours with a kick from the chipotle chillies.
